description:
Luffy is in an all-out, all-you-can-eat battle! As Cracker`s endless stream of Biscuit Warriors marches on, Luffy`s endless appetite is put to the test. Meanwhile, Reiju helps Sanji to straighten himself out before he meets his fiancée.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: A Battle of Limits! Luffy and the Infinite Biscuits!
Ein Kampf bis an die Grenzen! – Ruffy und die unendlichen Kekse
Genkai Shoubu: Luffy to Mugen Biscuit
Une batailles de limites. Luffy et les biscuits infinis
Битва на выносливость! Луффи и бесконечное печенье!
限界勝負 ルフィと無限ビスケット
